                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-deck" style="margin: 30px auto; text-align: center">
                <div class="col-lg-4 my-2" style="margin: auto">
                    <div class="card profile-card-2" style="">
                        <div class="card-img-block">
                            <img class="img-fluid"
                                src="https://i.pinimg.com/originals/a3/1b/1d/a31b1d35380af24948f54b42346225f6.png"
                                alt="Card image cap" style="
                                width: 150px;
                                height: 150px;
                                border-radius: 50%;
                                display: block;
                                margin: 15px auto 0;
                                object-fit: cover;
                            " />
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-body pt-5">
                            <h5 class="card-title">About Us</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                <strong>BookEx</strong> is your one stop solution
